title: Walk-In Closets, Extra Storage Available, Cable Ready
posting_body: ['Featuring luxury Eagan apartments, The Pointe at Cedar Grove is bringing a new era of living to the Twin Cities.', 'Just off of Highway 13 and Highway 77, The Pointe at Cedar Grove is only 20 minutes from both downtown Minneapolis and downtown St Paul.', 'The Pointe at Cedar Grove is conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment just a short distance away and is part of an excellent school district.', 'Offering one- and two-bedroom apartments, each unit includes a separate dining room, a balcony or patio, walk-in closets, and a gourmet kitchen.', 'Discover the secluded luxury of The Pointe at Cedar Grove.', '-Cable Ready', '-Laundry Facilities on Site', '-Clubroom', '-Walk-In Closets', '-Stainless Steel Appliances', '-Private Balcony or Patio', '-Walk-In Showers', '-Custom Cabinetry', '-Garages Available', '-Fitness Center', '-Furnished apartments available by CORT', '-Amenify - Professional Lifestyle Services for Residents', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Equal housing opportunity*']
